{"tid":948693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【非洲豬瘟】疫情殺到廣東 肉店職員唔憂生意：香港人習慣咗","createTime":"2018-12-20T09:04:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T14:33:46.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b0411a5731f9ce1989ad60f9bec860ee17e40135","tid":948693,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:04:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181220/large/1545280317_40ec.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181220%2Flarge%2F1545280317_40ec.png&h=3b40cdc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">肉檔職員劉先生稱，感覺街坊買豬肉的意慾略減，但長遠不擔心影響生意，因「過多幾日就無事，香港人習慣咗」。謝榮耀攝 </span><br />\n<br />\n內地爆發的非洲豬瘟疫情擴散，廣東珠海香洲區一個屠宰場就有11隻待宰生豬病發死亡。有業界擔心若疫情持續將影響活豬供應，推高本港豬肉價格。鵝頸橋肉枱職員劉先生指，感覺街坊買豬肉的意慾略減，「條街靜晒」，雖然街坊未有明言擔心，「啲人唔嚟就係啦」。但他對前景仍有信心，因豬肉是主食，「過多幾日就無事，香港人習慣咗」，且政府有檢疫「打晒印」，料疫情不會令港人避吃豬肉。<br />\n<br />\n劉指出，本港供應的豬肉主要來自內地，今日暫未見批發價增加。另一不願上鏡的肉枱職員指，今日來貨價略升，但不明顯，以往有疫情等因素都會影響供應，批發價會升一至兩成，最貴試過由每隻1,000多元，升至2,000多元。他稱難料今次疫情影響，零售價視情況調整，目前未加價。有肉枱職員說，市民難以肉眼分辨豬肉是否來自病豬，建議到相熟肉枱，「熟客嘅斬舊肉畀你都靚啲」。<br />\n<br />\n銅鑼灣街坊陳太說平日少吃豬肉，今日因兒子出差回港才買了20元，無留意有否加價，「買得少，無問價錢」。她稱今早有看新聞報道知道非洲豬瘟疫情擴散，但相信政府檢疫制度，在市面買到的豬肉應安全，會如常進食，日前外出吃冬至飯亦有吃豬肉。另一街坊沈女士亦稱「唔驚得咁多」，買了百多元豬肉用來炒菜及煲湯，「菜又話有事，雞又話有事，驚就唔使食喇！」<br />\n<br />\n香港豬肉行總商會理事長許偉堅早上在電台節目中表示，內地每日平均有4,000隻活豬供港，當中近80%來自廣東，但暫時未有供港豬場出現疫情。許強調，「好彩病毒對人和食物安全無影響，係豬會感染」，但勸喻市民應徹底煮熟豬肉進食。許表示，由於非洲豬瘟現時並無疫苗預防，一旦發現豬隻受感染，只能透過撲殺阻止蔓延。<br />\n<br />\n被問到疫情對豬價有否受影響，許稱港府對供港活豬的進口檢疫工作嚴謹，相信有病豬流入市面的機會極微，零售價格暫時尚算穩定，但假如有供港豬場都不幸中招，本港供應價格必定會受到影響，目前難以評估影響程度。他補充，內地為阻疫情擴散已要求活豬不能過省，「南方嘅豬不能北上，北方豬不能南下」，負責供港的內地豬場出口要提前7日通知檢疫局，並24小時全程監控運送，經多重檢查才能送到屠宰場。<br />\n<br />\n他指不排除少數病豬是在運送途中受感染，「中招都係食廚餘、潲水，但供港豬好早就改用乾料。」，形容過程「100%安全」。問到如何買到新鮮豬肉，他稱可留意肉色呈粉紅、不啞色。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181220/59050203\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59050203&d=JToigBLEqFuBXABKqoXuzGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=024505b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181220%2F59050203&h=ccf98569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181220/59050203</a>"},{"pid":"8d0e96936b1c52643c93333605ccb6c6c55b7aac","tid":948693,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ec0b7b0244d2c08344a87099389361465aa4e4e","tid":948693,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0e96936b1c52643c93333605ccb6c6c55b7aac","tid":948693,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"點同<br />\n大陸果D賤種黎"},{"pid":"4d3b1ba892d73d2ee2928a044b74056fff729398","tid":948693,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6f76da456bc73f132b3bf6dddc2bbbaff76f4ca","tid":948693,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d3b1ba892d73d2ee2928a044b74056fff729398","tid":948693,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ec0b7b0244d2c08344a87099389361465aa4e4e","tid":948693,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d0e96936b1c52643c93333605ccb6c6c55b7aac","tid":948693,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"點同<br />\n大陸果D賤種黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"死開D啦支那種<br />\n唔洗諗住痴埋黎等人當你係人<br />\n你賤種黎咋"},{"pid":"b83ee71d47bbd8ca498397a4eff9e2c892cc495a","tid":948693,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:18:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22055410280c2356c92f179ed8e8b959478f5f04","tid":948693,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:24:36.000Z","msg":"食就冇咩問題嘅，不過唔好帶入來香港感染香港啲港豬"},{"pid":"1727977cd16766d80cce4388638de55d89f82897","tid":948693,"uid":35581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f76da456bc73f132b3bf6dddc2bbbaff76f4ca","tid":948693,"uid":2772,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d3b1ba892d73d2ee2928a044b74056fff729398","tid":948693,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ec0b7b0244d2c08344a87099389361465aa4e4e","tid":948693,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:15:15.000Z","msg":"點同<br />\n大陸果D賤種黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:17:24.000Z","msg":"死開D啦支那種<br />\n唔洗諗住痴埋黎等人當你係人<br />\n你賤種黎咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T09:25:45.000Z","msg":"屌得好"},{"pid":"d50e6f97f2e84dfdabe4f0ebebc1c39634363aa8","tid":948693,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:35:44.000Z","msg":"麥記發霉肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日輻射零食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n塑化劑奶茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a49816f7569eb3cecb5895a22c837d35be4caec","tid":948693,"uid":107574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wgi8PQg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwgi8PQg.gif&h=e10f760c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"565827ef9bb85f3c856af155e46b5643235a91f1","tid":948693,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:45:10.000Z","msg":"整曬做冰鮮"},{"pid":"919f3ac0196cd1141a8bd18ce7927ebb841bb0fa","tid":948693,"uid":200328,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:47:52.000Z","msg":"大家估下幾會傳埋黎香港, 跟住又幾時開始屈係香港傳染支那<br />\n沙士都係咁屈<br />\n<br />\n日本同台灣發現支那人帶支那豬過去好明顯係想傳染過去比人, 之後再屈人傳染支那<br />\n成個局黎<br />\n香港無捉隨時已經拎左唔知幾多支那豬肉入黎<br />\n依家懷疑當時沙士都係呢招<br />\n傳染疫症搞冧你經濟, 再屈係你傳染支那"},{"pid":"38e0a21e322ddfd5f5af8e00645dc3b12085eff6","tid":948693,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a49816f7569eb3cecb5895a22c837d35be4caec","tid":948693,"uid":107574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:41:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wgi8PQg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwgi8PQg.gif&h=e10f760c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2ec9105336e0f29d65cc2a288e285c853dca8e0","tid":948693,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T14:33:46.000Z","msg":"感染埋啲港豬仲好啦，反正同發豬瘟冇分別"}]}